{"lemma":"مُنْقَلَبِ","slug":"مُنْقَلَبِ","root":"ق.ل.ب","root_slug":"ق-ل-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ق-ل-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"مُنْقَلَبِ","root":"قلب","pos":"N","occurrence_count":3},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n36091"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8F%D9%86%D9%92%D9%82%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"capsized"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"reversed"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the active participle of اِنْقَلَبَ (inqalaba, “to be turned upside down”)."},"ipa":["/mun.qa.lib/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n36091","headword_ar":"مُنْقَلَبٌ","root":"qlb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"An inf. n. of 7 [q. v.]. (S, O, K, TA.) ―         -b2-  And also a n. of place from the same [for which Freytag seems to have found in a copy of the S"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muqal~abN","text_ar":"مُقَلَّبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", a mistranscription], (S, O, K, TA,) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"munoSarafN","text_ar":"مُنْصَرَفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) [As a n. of place it signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A place in which a thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"person, is,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"becomes, altered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"changed, from its,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his, mode,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"manner, of being:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and hence,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place in which a thing becomes inverted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"turned upside-down,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c. ―         -b3-  Hence, also, (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"final place to which one is translated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"removed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"by death; and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mutaqal~abN","text_ar":"مُتَقَلَّبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":".] One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kul~u A^aHad yaSiyru A_ilaY munoqalabihi","text_ar":"كُلُّ اَحَد يَصِيرُ اـِلَى مُنْقَلَبِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mutaqal~abihi","text_ar":"مُتَقَلَّبِهِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Every one reaches,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"will reach, his final place to which he is to be translated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"removed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) ―         -b4-  [And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A place to which one returns from a journey"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]"}],"source_refs":["S","O","K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}